    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/dbdocsconcept1.dita">The NextGen Trading Card Game (NXTCG) features exclusive collectible cards inspired
        by the Rocket Software NextGen Academy and its Rocketeers. The platform empowers you to buy
